Available timezones origin:
tzdata / /usr/share/zoneinfo/zone.tab

Timezones translations:
https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gnome-control-center/-/tree/main/panels/system/datetime/po-timezones?ref_type=heads
lconvert -locations none --target-language de_DE \
    /home/superandy/data/tmp/oe-zenux/tmp-glibc/work/cortexa9t2hf-neon-mortsgna-linux-gnueabi/xfce4-datetime-setter/3.32.2-r0/git/panels/datetime/po-timezones/de.po \
    -o /home/superandy/data/tmp/de_DE.ts

DBus
gdbus introspect --xml --system --dest org.freedesktop.timedate1 --object-path /org/freedesktop/timedate1
dbus-monitor --system "type='signal', member='PropertiesChanged', path='/org/freedesktop/timedate1'"

DBus -> Qt
https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qdbusxml2cpp.html
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aCkzCVbiTjw


